                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>True to our vision of helping employees reach their full potential, AHORA emphasizes mentorship and networking opportunities.&lt;/p>&lt;p>Our efforts include:&lt;/p>&lt;p>&lt;ul> &lt;li>Hosting “Café con Leche” talks with AbbVie leadership&lt;/li> &lt;li>Offering seminars led by university partners&lt;/li> &lt;li>Collaborating with external organizations&lt;/li> &lt;li>Supporting employees new to AbbVie with orientation activities&lt;/li> &lt;/ul>&lt;/p>"/>
