                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>Community outreach is part of AHORA’s fabric. True to our vision of building a stronger workforce, we are committed to supporting the communities in our own backyard.&lt;/p>&lt;p>&lt;ul> &lt;li>We’ve embedded with a high school in our hometown community of Waukegan, IL and support their students with mentoring along with career exploration, including encouraging their students to apply to our internships&lt;/li> &lt;li>We engage in various volunteer efforts, including mentorship for students from diverse backgrounds&lt;/li> &lt;li>We partner with other organizations to find ways to collaborate and benchmark on Latino ERG initiatives and activities and provide networking and mentorship workshops&lt;/li> &lt;/ul>&lt;/p>&lt;p>AHORA is proud to support community organizations in partnership with the AbbVie Foundation.&lt;/p>"/>
